227 Gregory Hall
May 17, 1955
Mr. Dahlenburg:
Will you please transfer necessary items
from the trust Kellogg Tape Network account to the
HkEB Revolving account between now and July 1, and
any such items as necessary to keep the trust fund
in balance.
sincerely yours.
Frank E. Schooley
SeSijSr. H. J. Skornia
